        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I would expect these two sets of steps to yield the same result, but they don't. Might be relevant?\r\n\r\n#### setlocal winhighlight\r\n\r\n1. `nvim --clean`\r\n2. `:setlocal winhighlight=Normal:Search`\r\n3. `:copen`\r\n\r\n![2022-04-27_02-58-26_Alacritty](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/21299126/165493393-d180c067-c195-47e0-b2ed-a6232d4c63ca.png)\r\n\r\n#### vim.wo.winhighlight\r\n\r\n1. `nvim --clean`\r\n2. `:lua vim.wo.winhighlight = 'Normal:Search'`\r\n3. `:copen`\r\n\r\n![2022-04-27_02-59-27_Alacritty](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/21299126/165493551-9f87f9ab-5e53-4b72-a3fe-dc2ad7405b1e.png)\r\n",
